BERLIN - FEBRUARY 12: Actress Katja Riemann (R) and friend actress Nadine Schori kiss at the Cinema for Peace Charity Gala on February 12, 2007 in Berlin, Germany. The gala is traditionally held during the Berlin International Film Festival (Berlinale). (Photo by Sean Gallup/Getty Images)
